Modified QuanTest2


# Nextflow
quantest2.nf                Nextflow pipeline to retrieve N informative sequences + run QuanTest2
nextflow.config             Nextflow configuration file

# Scripts
bin/get_refANDinformative_seqs.py       Retrieve N sequences (reference + (N-ref) informative sequences) from an given fasta file <seq or msa>. 
bin/quantest2Local.py       Modified QuanTest2's python script. Source paper: https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btz552
bin/runpsipred              Modified PSIPRED script. Source: https://github.com/psipred/psipred

# Docker
docker/Dockerfile           Dockerfile. It will create a container with DeepMSA (includes the a3m2mtx.pl script and other binary files), PSIPRED (secondary structure prediction), QuanTest2 and T-coffee.


